trans-unit.source: Transforms XML data using an XSLT style sheet.
trans-unit.target: Overfører XML-dataene ved hjelp av en XSLT-stilarket.

trans-unit.source: The XslCompiledTransform class is an XSLT processor that supports the XSLT 1.0 syntax.
trans-unit.target: Klassen XslCompiledTransform er en XSLT-prosessor som støtter syntaksen XSLT 1.0.

trans-unit.source: It is a new implementation and includes performance gains when compared to the obsolete <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslTransform> class.
trans-unit.target: Det er en ny implementering og inkluderer bedre sammenlignet med foreldet <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslTransform>klasse.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslTransform>

trans-unit.source: The structure of the XslCompiledTransform class is very similar to the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslTransform> class.
trans-unit.target: Strukturen i klassen XslCompiledTransform ligner <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslTransform>klasse.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslTransform>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Load%2A> method loads and compiles the style sheet, while the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A> method executes the XSLT transform.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Load%2A>metoden laster inn og kompilerer stilen arket, under den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A>metoden utfører XSLT-transformeringen.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Load%2A>

trans-unit.source: Support for the XSLT `document()` function and embedded script blocks are disabled by default.
trans-unit.target: Støtte for XSLT `document()` funksjonen og innebygde Skriptblokkene er deaktivert som standard.

trans-unit.source: These features can be enabled by creating an <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltSettings> object and passing it to the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Load%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Disse funksjonene kan aktiveres ved å opprette en <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltSettings>objekt og sende den til den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Load%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Load%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltSettings>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Using the XslCompiledTransform Class](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Migrating From the XslTransform Class](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [ved hjelp av XslCompiledTransform klassen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [migrasjon fra XslTransform klasse.](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Security Considerations When creating an application that uses the XslCompiledTransform class, you should be aware of the following items and their implications: - XSLT scripting is disabled by default.
trans-unit.target: Sikkerhet informasjon når du oppretter et program som bruker klassen XslCompiledTransform, kan du bør være klar over følgende elementer og hvordan virker:-XSLT skripting er deaktivert som standard.

trans-unit.source: XSLT scripting should be enabled only if you require script support and you are working in a fully trusted environment.
trans-unit.target: XSLT-skripting må være aktivert hvis du trenger skript støtte og du arbeider i et miljø med fullstendig klarerte.

trans-unit.source: - The XSLT `document()` function is disabled by default.
trans-unit.target: XSLT- `document()` funksjonen er deaktivert som standard.

trans-unit.source: If you enable the `document()` function, restrict the resources that can be accessed by passing an <xref:System.Xml.XmlSecureResolver> object to the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du aktiverer den `document()` fungere, Begrens ressurser som kan nås ved å sende en <xref:System.Xml.XmlSecureResolver>objekt i <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A>metode.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A> </xref:System.Xml.XmlSecureResolver>

trans-unit.source: - Extension objects are enabled by default.
trans-unit.target: -Utvidelse objekter er aktivert som standard.

trans-unit.source: If an <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltArgumentList> object containing extension objects is passed to the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A> method, they are utilized.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltArgumentList>objekt som inneholder utvidelsen objekter som er sendt til den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A>metoden de benyttet.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltArgumentList>

trans-unit.source: - XSLT style sheets can include references to other files and embedded script blocks.
trans-unit.target: -XSLT stilark kan inneholde referanser til andre filer og innebygde Skriptblokkene.

trans-unit.source: A malicious user can exploit this by supplying you with data or style sheets that when executed can cause your system to process until the computer runs low on resources.
trans-unit.target: En bruker med onde hensikter kan utnytte dette ved å oppgi du med data eller stil ark som når den kjøres kan føre til at datamaskinen for å behandle før datamaskinen kjører lite ressurser.

trans-unit.source: - XSLT applications that run in a mixed trust environment can result in style sheet spoofing.
trans-unit.target: -XSLT programmer som kjører i et miljø i blandet klarering kan medføre stil arket forfalskning.

trans-unit.source: For example, a malicious user can load an object with a harmful style sheet and hand it off to another user who subsequently calls the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A> method and executes the transformation.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en ondsinnet bruker kan laste inn et objekt med en skadelig stilarket og leverer den til en annen bruker som senere kaller den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A>metoden og utfører transformeringen.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A>

trans-unit.source: These security issues can be mitigated by not enabling scripting or the `document()` function unless the style sheet comes from a trusted source, and by not accepting XslCompiledTransform objects, XSLT style sheets, or XML source data from an untrusted source.
trans-unit.target: Disse sikkerhetsproblemer kan begrenses ved ikke å aktivere skripting eller `document()` fungerer med mindre stilarket som kommer fra en pålitelig kilde, og ved å ikke godta XslCompiledTransform objekter, XSLT stilark eller XML-kilde data fra en uklarert kilde.
